questions.quote: If only there was something in your head to control the things you say.
I do! I do! I do! I do! Ugh, like I can really chase you. I'm carrying a litter.
Well, when you do, just let me know. I'll be right over there on the edge of my seat.
Yeah. Yeah. Definitely, well it definitely took me by surprise, but I'm okay.
All right, look, I hate this as much as you, but if it makes you feel better, it's all your fault.
...So I think Alan will become the yardstick against which all future boyfriends will be measured.
Wait!! Where are you going?! What are you doing?! No!! Wait!! God!! Why am I always pregnant when she does that?!
Y'know, I gotta tell ya, this really does put in a better mood.
All right, all right, if you insist on doing this, at least let me help you.
Oh, what do you know? No one's going up to you and saying, "Hi, is that your nostril? Mind if we push this pot roast through it?"
